  "page": "Westwatch-by-the-Bridge",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_North.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The north and the location of the Westwatch-by-the-Bridge\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of the Westwatch-by-the-Bridge\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/400px-The_North.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/600px-The_North.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/800px-The_North.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 12.2%; left: 52.2%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 9px; font-size: 9px;\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of the Westwatch-by-the-Bridge\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/9px-Wolff2.PNG\" title=\"Westwatch-by-the-Bridge\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/14px-Wolff2.PNG 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/18px-Wolff2.PNG 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Westwatch-by-the-Bridge</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> and the location of the Westwatch-by-the-Bridge\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Westwatch-by-the-Bridge</b> is the westernmost castle of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>, located near the <a href=\"/index.php/Gorge\" title=\"Gorge\">Gorge</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Bridge_of_Skulls\" title=\"Bridge of Skulls\">Bridge of Skulls</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_westwatch-by-the-bridge.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_westwatch-by-the-bridge.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> East of the abandoned castle is the <a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Tower\" title=\"Shadow Tower\">Shadow Tower</a>, the westernmost of the inhabited castles of the Watch.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_shadow_tower.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_shadow_tower.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> places Westwatch north of the Gorge and west of the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>  <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i> depicts Westwatch south of the Gorge and just east of the Bridge of Skulls, where the Wall ends.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf_beyond_the_wall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf_beyond_the_wall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westwatch-by-the-Bridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Westwatch_by_the_Bridge.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d6/Westwatch_by_the_Bridge.jpg/350px-Westwatch_by_the_Bridge.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"263\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d6/Westwatch_by_the_Bridge.jpg/525px-Westwatch_by_the_Bridge.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d6/Westwatch_by_the_Bridge.jpg/700px-Westwatch_by_the_Bridge.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Westwatch_by_the_Bridge.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Westwatch-by-the-Bridge by Marc Simonetti © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westwatch-by-the-Bridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Bowen_Marsh\" title=\"Bowen Marsh\">Bowen Marsh</a> leads men of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> in defending the region from <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Fight_at_the_Bridge_of_Skulls\" title=\"Fight at the Bridge of Skulls\">fight at the Bridge of Skulls</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westwatch-by-the-Bridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord Commander <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> has Westwatch re-garrisoned with a small company of men from the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_westwatch-by-the-bridge.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_westwatch-by-the-bridge.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westwatch-by-the-Bridge&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_westwatch-by-the-bridge.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_westwatch-by-the-bridge.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_westwatch-by-the-bridge.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Westwatch-by-the-Bridge.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_shadow_tower.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_shadow_tower.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Shadow Tower.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Map_of_Beyond_The_Wall\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Map of Beyond The Wall\">Map of Beyond the Wall</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf_beyond_the_wall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf_beyond_the_wall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Beyond the Wall.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_75\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 75\">Chapter 75</a>, Samwell IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tb